    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride that has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has plenty of life left in it! While it\u2019s seen some love over the years, it still runs beautifully and looks fantastic on the road. It's been well-cared for and is ready for its next adventure. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the new-car price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it!",
