    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of reliability and premium comfort. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only minor cosmetic stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker environment featuring supple leather seating with no rips or stains, and all power features\u2014including the ice-cold dual-zone climate control and sunroof\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a documented service history, including a recent oil change, brake inspection, and a fresh set of tires with plenty of tread remaining. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and requires nothing but a new owner. Includes two sets of keys and all original manuals.",
      "price": 34800.0,
