    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has been really well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable, smooth journey! It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and is just waiting for its next adventure. If you're looking for a solid car that won't let you down, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 33500.0,
