    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's engineering peak, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution during spirited drives. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's known stress points. The suspension retains its tactile feedback, providing the neutral handling balance this platform is renowned for. While the exterior and interior show minor patina reflective of its mileage, the powertrain remains robust, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience.",
